{"tid":1346002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：是可忍，孰不可忍！","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:40:41.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"afd4e7667ad7cb6625c8bed2b1122d1be1930476","tid":1346002,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:16:51.000Z","msg":"是可忍，孰不可忍！<br />\n這批暴徒<span style=\"color: red;\">居心明顯，歹毒心腸</span>，肆意侮辱國家尊嚴，祇為害死香港，破壞一國兩制，毀滅法治！這些人將香港打爛後又逃之夭夭，不會負責任！<span style=\"color: red;\">最後由全香港人埋單！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">他們騎劫了反修例的遊行示威，去進行對香港毀滅性的行動</span>。各位支持和平，愛護香港，包括曾參加反修例遊行的香港人，請勇敢地與這些<span style=\"color: red;\">惡行</span>切割，一齊讉責此等<span style=\"color: red;\">惡霸行為</span>，支持香港警隊嚴格執法，把他們繩之於法！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XqMhjmE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXqMhjmE.png&h=155c33cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03eb1be91f3d46e17ff0fde1f92b9d756d9a7f06","tid":1346002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07